	Nonfunctional domains:

		- (www.)kobobooks.com	*
		- blog.kobobooks.com		(prints "Thank you for taking part")

		- ptbr.kobobooks.com *

			- These paths redirect to http:

				- android$
				- apps$
				- blackberry$
				- default.aspx$
				- egiftcards$
				- ereaders$
				- free_ebooks$
				- Gifting$
				- Gifting/Start.aspx$
				- iphone$
				- lists$
				- lists/New_Releases/GLES0et0ik-Asyf9eaGKWQ-1.html
				- palmpre$
				- readinglife$
				- search$
				- search/search.html
				- smartphones$

	* Redirects to http


	Problematic domains:

		- ecimages.kobobooks.com	(akamai)

-->
<ruleset name="Kobo (partial)">

	<target host="kobobooks.com" />
	<target host="*.kobobooks.com" />


	<rule from="^http://(assets|merch)\.kobobooks\.com/"
		to="https://$1.kobobooks.com/" />

	<rule from="^https?://(?:ec)?images\.kobobooks\.com/"
		to="https://images.kobobooks.com/" />

</ruleset>